headline: Raymond James Hires $5 Billion Advisor Team Serving Institutional Clients
summary: Raymond James Financial  recruited two advisors who previously managed more than $5 billion in assets, the company said Thursday.  Advisors Scott Burnett and Peter Kelson joined a unit of Raymond James & Associates, the company’s employee broker-dealer, in Cottonwood Heights, Utah.  A representative for Raymond James declined to comment further.
